{"type":"message","id":"0bd66a13","parentId":"5bc8a897","timestamp":"2026-05-22T02:55:20.597Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The owner wants to change 赵嘉浩's (zhaojiahao, id=2068) permissions from Developer to Reporter (20) across all 5 repos. I need to use the `update` command on each repo.\n\nLet me check the syntax - from the skill, update is:\n```\nPUT /api/v4/projects/{project_id}/members/{user_id}\nBody: access_level={10|20|30|40}\n```\n\nAnd the script has `update <id> <user> <level>`.\n\nReporter = 20. Let me do all 5 repos.\n\nActually, the `batch` command only supports adding. For modifying existing members, I need to update each repo individually. Or actually, looking at the script more carefully - the `batch` command adds members. Since 赵嘉浩 already has Developer (30) on all 5 repos (I just added him), I need to update each one to Reporter (20).\n\nLet me run 5 update commands in parallel.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，把赵嘉浩从 Developer 降为 Reporter（只读）。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_SyUjw1Lzjlw0AWOZEqel1610","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"node C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\git_permission.mjs update 5058 zhaojiahao reporter","timeout":15}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_01_SsDZD3yChmseNhMRBZcw9871","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"node C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\git_permission.mjs update 4710 zhaojiahao reporter","timeout":15}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_02_D21k5etWIaJzQZmUi1C47709","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"node C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\git_permission.mjs update 5048 zhaojiahao reporter","timeout":15}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_03_gGXwau4VsRGKtEkpQCLu3644","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"node C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\git_permission.mjs update 5145 zhaojiahao reporter","timeout":15}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_04_ETYXwK71eDtS1hhJy