{"type":"message","id":"85a2eca5","parentId":"92fa3da0","timestamp":"2026-05-22T02:57:20.421Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The owner wants me to remember that from now on, when adding colleagues to GitLab, the default permission should be Reporter (20) instead of Developer (30). I should update the relevant memory and skill files to reflect this default.\n\nLet me update:\n1. MEMORY.md - the gitlab-permission section\n2. TOOLS.md - the relevant section about git permissions\n3. The SKILL.md for gitlab-permission\n\nActually, let me think about what to update. The SKILL.md is the skill file - I should update that to reflect the new default. But SKILL.md is at `~/.openclaw/plugin-skills/gitlab-permission/SKILL.md`. Actually, skill files can be updated by the skill-creator skill. But actually since the owner just gave an instruction, I should update my memory and the relevant config files.\n\nLet me update MEMORY.md and TOOLS.md with this new default, and also the git_permission script's batch command if it has a hardcoded level.\n\nActually let me check what the batch command does - it says \"给 XX 加项目权限\" adds Developer(30). Now the default should be Reporter(20).\n\nLet me update:\n1. MEMORY.md - add this note\n2. TOOLS.md - update the batch description to mention new default\n3. The gitlab-permission SKILL.md - update the default level\n\nActually I should be careful about modifying SKILL.md. Let me check if it's appropriate to modify it. The skill says when someone says \"给 XX 加项目权限\" to add Developer(30) to 5 repos. Now the boss wants the default to be Reporter.\n\nLet me update:\n1. MEMORY.md \n2. TOOLS.md - update the default in the batch section\n3. SKILL.md - update the default level\n\nLet me make the edits.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"收到，以后默认 Reporter。记下来。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_0NfwMI1Pm9CyGTDnwjQl9061","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\MEMORY.md","edits":[{"oldText":"## GitLab 权限管理 Skill（2026-05-21 更新）","newText":"## GitLab 权限管理 Skill（2026-05-22 更新）"},{"oldText":"- 权限等级：10=Guest, 20=Reporter, 30=Developer, 40=Maintainer, 50=Owner\n- 可管理项目：10 个（Maintainer+），含 1v1/config(5058)、nightoffullmoon(2751) 等","newText":"- 权限等级：10=Guest, 20=Reporter, 30=Developer, 40=Maintainer, 50=Owner\n- **默认权限 = Reporter(20)**：给同事开权限一律 Reporter，除非主人明确要求更高级别\n- 可管理项目：10 个（Maintainer+），含 1v1/config(5058)、nightoffullmoon(2751) 等"}]}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_01_9JXsvX5yFy3iEWmYvjrf5313","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\TOOLS.md","edits":[{"oldText":"### Skills (My Custom Workflows)","newText":"**默认权限：** 给同事开 GitLab 权限时统一切到 Reporter(20)，不擅自给 Developer。如果主人明确要求更高权限再按需提权。\n\n### Skills (My Custom Workflows)"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1538,"output":826,"cacheRead":32768,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35132,"cost":{"input":0.00021532000000000002,"output":0.00023128000000000002,"cacheRead":0.000917504,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001364104}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779418632420,"responseId":"0bc5ad8e-8fd8-4109-a158-1303c2a88c54"}}
