{"type":"message","id":"5f8955c6","parentId":"6acfb442","timestamp":"2026-05-22T04:21:25.282Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK so the pipeline DID run asset building. The logs show:\n1. Bundle files encrypted (multiple .bundle.encrypt files)\n2. Patch manifest created (PackageManifest_SoloPackage_1.1.015.json etc.)\n3. Build report created (BuildReport_SoloPackage_1.1.015.json)\n4. Patch files copied to output directory\n5. \"构建成功\" - Build successful\n6. Upload CDN\n\nSo the bundle building step DID run fully. But maybe the owner is observing it's too fast because of incremental/delta builds. Only 8.7 seconds for BuildAssetBundles (3 samples).\n\nHowever, wait - looking at the log output again, I see the \"Bundle文件加密完成\" files but don't see messages about the actual BuildPipeline.BuildAssetBundles start or progress. Let me look at what's between the incremental build success and the encryption step.\n\nAlso, I see that the bundle version is 1.1.015, but the output version from the pipeline was 1.0.41. So there's a mismatch - the pipeline's hot update went to `D:/cdn_solo\\update\\Android\\Test1\\1.0.41` but the bundle building is outputting to `Bundles/Test1/Android/SoloPackage/1.1.015`.\n\nActually, looking more carefully:\n- The bundle pipeline built to: `Bundles/Test1/Android/SoloPackage/1.1.015`\n- The CDN pipeline then uploads and sets up local test env at `D:/cdn_solo\\update\\Android\\Test1\\1.0.41`\n\nThese might be different version numbers. 1.1.015 is the bundle version, and 1.0.41 is the hot update version.\n\nAnyway, the pipeline DID run the bundle building step. The issue might be that the owner is looking at Unity's output and doesn't see it because the incremental build is fast, or the logs don't clearly show the build step.\n\nLet me share the findings with the owner and suggest checking the bundle output directory directly.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"主人，我查了流水线日志，**打资源包那步确实运行了**，但因为是增量构建模式，速度很快（8.7s），可能看起来像没运行。\n\n日志关键信息：\n\n```\nIncrementalBuild pipeline build succeed!        ← 增量构建成功\nBundle文件加密完成：...xxx.bundle.encrypt        ← 多个bundle已加密\n创建补丁清单文件：PackageManifest_SoloPackage_1.1.015.json\n创建补丁清单哈希文件\n构建成功：Bundles/Test1/Android/SoloPackage/1.1.015\n上传CDN（2.29s）\n[HotUpdate] 本地测试环境已准备就绪: D:/cdn_solo\\update\\Android\\Test1\\1.0.41\n[Performance] BuildAssetBundles: 3 samples, Total 8.697s\n```\n\n构建输出在：\n- **Bundle目录：** `E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\Bundles\\Test1\\Android\\SoloPackage\\1.1.015`\n- **本地测试环境：** `D:\\cdn_solo\\update\\Android\\Test1\\1.0.41`\n\n**觉得\"没运行\"可能是因为默认增量模式太快了？** 如果想让每次看到完整的构建过程，可以切一次**全量构建**（清理 Bundles 缓存），不过那样每次就要多花不少时间。你想现在跑一次全量确认下有没有问题吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1807,"output":769,"cacheRead":56576,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":59152,"cost":{"input":0.00025298000000000003,"output":0.00021532000000000002,"cacheRead":0.001584128,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0020524280000000002}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779423676402,"responseId":"d3b76f29-e241-43b6-a40a-ac5e64c9e268"}}
