{"type":"message","id":"77ed74c8","parentId":"a2db5037","timestamp":"2026-05-22T10:36:40.483Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The owner says \"更新qa测试服服务器\". This is about updating the QA test server, which is the server-side DevOps pipeline (not the client hot update). From my TOOLS.md:\n\n### 更新服务器（服务端 DevOps）\n**触发指令:** \"更新qa服\" / \"更新qa服务器\" / \"更新1v1_qa服\" / \"更新1v1_test服\"\n\n\"更新qa测试服服务器\" - this is server-side, dest = 1v1_qa.\n\nThe process:\n1. Check DevOps Cookie is valid\n2. Use Playwright to open pipeline page, click \"启动新构建\"\n3. Change dest to 1v1_qa, keep other variables default\n4. Submit trigger, confirm build running\n5. Notify owner when done\n\nThis is a long task (>10s) so I should spawn a sub-agent.\n\nLet me check the DevOps skill or memory for more details about the exact URL and steps.\n\nActually, from MEMORY.md:\n- Pipeline ID: `p-f78c977835c84b71a6d58b4746cd1c4a`\n- DevOps pipeline for 1v1 server update\n- Need to check DevOps Cookie validity first\n- No need to notify group, just notify the requester (owner)\n\nLet me spawn a sub-agent to handle this.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\"更新qa测试服服务器\" → 懂，服务端 1v1_qa 服，走 DevOps 流水线。开子进程处理。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_paCZqfOQ8Zzjk82jQLQN5575","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"label":"devops-1v1_qa","mode":"run","task":"执行 DevOps 服务端更新流水线，更新 1v1_qa 服（1v1 QA测试服）\n\n**流程：**\n1. 检查 DevOps Cookie 是否有效（读取 `workspace/devops_cookies.json`）\n2. 用 Playwright 打开流水线页面 `https://devops.tencent.com/p/team-1e6d48f4846c421d6c827a5a9b0a71f2/pipeline/p-f78c977835c84b71a6d58b4746cd1c4a/build`\n3. 点击「启动新构建」\n4. 找到 dest 参数，改为 `1v1_qa`，其他变量保持默认\n5. 点击提交/确认，确认构建进入运行中状态\n6. 等待构建完成（轮询状态，可能需要几分钟）\n7. 构建完成后直接通知指派人（主人）\n\n**注意：**\n- 不要在命令行里拼含 @ 的文本\n- 如果 DevOps Cookie 失效，需要退出脚本并通知主人重新登录"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":14391,"output":625,"cacheRead":44800,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":59816,"cost":{"input":0.00201474,"output":0.00017500000000000003,"cacheRead":0.0012544,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00344414}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779446192575,"responseId":"4dc66fcd-3dfe-4842-900e-266b10cf8020"}}
